rental.description:
You wont want to miss this one! This stunning, spacious, 2 storey home with 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and inground pool, is located in the prestigious Crestwood Heights Estate, at Casuarina Drive, Crestwood Heights, Molendinar 4214, the best home currently available and within walking distance to the new Gold Coast Hospital, Griffiths University, shopping centres and local schools. Features include: Master Bedroom Suite 4 further double bedrooms, 3 full sized bathrooms (2 ensuited) Inground pool, fully fenced Large flat separate lawned area for the children or pets Ducted air conditioning Formal lounge and dining First Floor Parents Retreat Gourmet Kitchen with Granite Benchtops Crimsafe screens Vacuumaid Undercover Alfresco area Double garage Plenty of storage Fully fenced, landscaped gardens
At Crestwood Heights, you're only minutes to local schools such as Aquinas College, Guardian Angels Primary School and Trinity Lutheran College. You're also within walking distance to Griffiths University and the new Gold Coast Hospital (currently under construction), close to great golf at Parkwood International Golf Course, and within easy access of the Nerang and Helensvale Railway Stations. Southport CBD( Australia Fair) and Ashmore Shopping Centres, and Marina Mirage and Pacific Fair are just a short drive away. Crsetwood Heights is only 10 minutes to the Gold Coast's spectacular sandy beaches and everything that you could want for a holiday destination. Incorporating over 9 hectares of parkland, Crestwood heights has been planned with attention to detail including walkways, children's playgrounds and parks. Enjoy the privacy of your own neighbourhood and the beauty of nature, yet be conveniently close to all the established services you require. Such are the rewards of living in a haven like Crestwood Heights. A rare find amongst the beauty of the Gold Coast.
